{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require companies to clearly display a contact section with email & phone number",
        "additional_details": "We feel many companies make it hard to contact them, hiding contact details behind bots or buried menus. This can leave people - especially the elderly, disabled, or those less tech-savvy - frustrated and unsupported when things go wrong. Everyone deserves access to real help. We think clear contact info can help build trust, fairness, and accountability.",
        "background": "Make it a legal requirement for all UK companies to clearly display a \u201cContact Us\u201d section with a working UK telephone number and email address on both their website and mobile app, so customers can easily get support from a real person when needed.",
